---
import Layout from '../../../../site-layouts/Layout.astro';
import GeekSpellBaseStyles from '../../../../components/geekspell/GeekSpellBaseStyles.astro';

const YT_ID = 'rMjxLyl2-B8';
const YT_EMBED = `https://www.youtube.com/embed/${YT_ID}`;
const YT_WATCH = `https://youtu.be/${YT_ID}`;
---

<Layout title="EP05 · The Acceptance Loop | GeekSpell" lang="en">
  <GeekSpellBaseStyles />
  <main class="gs-ep-page">
    <div class="gs-wrap">
      <p class="gs-crumb">
        <a href="/en/">Archive</a> · <a href="/en/geekspell/">GeekSpell</a> · EP05
      </p>
      <p class="gs-eyebrow">GeekSpell literacy EP05 · English · Acceptance</p>
      <h1>The Acceptance Loop</h1>
      <p class="gs-lead">
        Before bigger teams and skills, close the loop of acceptance — or every agent run ends in
        “looks fine.”
      </p>
      <div class="gs-player">
        <iframe
          src={YT_EMBED}
          title="GeekSpell EP05 EN"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="gs-links">
        <a href="/en/geekspell/ep04-scope-split/">← EP04 Scope split</a>
        ·
        <a href="/en/geekspell/ep06-agent-team/">EP06 Agent team →</a>
        ·
        <a href="/ja/geekspell/ep05-acceptance-loop/">日本語 EP05</a>
        ·
        <a href={YT_WATCH} target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>
      </p>
      <section class="gs-body">
        <h2>What you will learn (step by step)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Why shipping without a definition of done fails</li>
          <li>The loop: define done → run → check → fix / roll back → accept</li>
          <li>Step 1: checklist before you prompt</li>
          <li>Step 2: green / yellow / red scoring</li>
          <li>Step 3: the human owns the final acceptance gate</li>
          <li>A five-field template you can copy today</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Series path</h2>
        <p>
          EP04 scope → <strong>EP05 acceptance</strong> → EP06 agent team → EP07 skill &amp; workflow
          → EP08 one-page loop.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
